com.ashraf.course.machinelearning.id3decisiontree.dataStructures

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ashraf.course.machinelearning.id3decisiontree.dataStructures.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    Entry class is a data structure class which is used to store both training and testing data entries in the project. Entry class stores ID, DNA sequence and class of each data entry.

    version 1.0.0
